<p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">3</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">月</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">8</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">日上午，江西软件职业技术大学党委理论学习中心组学习（扩大）会在行政楼一楼会议室召开。会议由党委书记、督导专员江延湖主持。党委领导班子成员、党群部门负责人、党总支书记</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">和</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">直属党支部书记参加会议。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/ahead_party_web/img/2024-03-09%2016%3A49%3A186add669ca57f96a30cdb6d9067c2380.jpg?Expires=2025334158&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=z1zHgAyLKEKCyyp8i3OW9TLvzNI%3D" width="600" height="400" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 600px; height: 400px;" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">会议传达学习了全国两会关于政府工作报告和安全生产方面关于习近平总书记对江西新余市渝水区一临街店铺火灾事故作出重要指示和省委省人民政府、省委教育工委省教育厅关于安全生产工作的会议精神；集中学习了习近平总书记关于新质生产力的重要论述、全国、全省教育工作会议精神、习近平总书记在二十届中央纪委三次全会上发表重要讲话、江西省政府年度工作报告和江西教育工作领导小组第一次会议精神。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">会议指出，要坚持以习近平新时代中国特色社会主义思想为指导，全面贯彻党的教育方针，聚焦</span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">“走在前、勇争先、善作为”的要求，坚持立德树人的根本任务，弘扬教育家精神，牢记自身职责，践行为党育人、为国育才的初心使命，切实把全国两会精神学习好、领会透、把握准，并落实到办学治校各方面。学校将进一步坚持“党管教育”，加强党建引领；进一步强化“依法治校”，提升办学水平；进一步落实“以生为本”，服务学生成长成才；进一步倡导“以师为尊”，聚力改革发展稳定；充分彰显办学特色和优势，围绕电子信息产业链，在本科层次职业教育办学范式上多总结凝练出鲜活的实证经验和案例参考。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">会议强调，安全是一切工作的基础和前提，各部门要时刻将校园安全放在首位，要做好安全隐患大排查工作，进一步提高校园安全、政治安全、意识形态安全、风险防控意识，提升防范化解风险的能力水平，切实维护学校安全稳定。</span></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><img src="https://aheadedu.oss-cn-shenzhen.aliyuncs.com/school_branch/ahead_party_web/img/2024-03-09%2016%3A48%3A135f524f6177598e054fe84bde7687650.jpg?Expires=2025334093&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI4GEYjbEWU9Knh4iN17fd&Signature=aHd8E%2BUnnbZpy%2BxU6o4TejorwT0%3D" width="600" height="450" style="box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px none; vertical-align: middle; margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; list-style-type: none; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; filter: saturate(1.1); display: block; width: 600px; height: 450px;" border="0" vspace="0" title="" alt=""/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0pt 0pt 0.0001pt; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: Calibri; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; line-height: 28pt; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24pt; text-align: justify;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 18px; font-family: 宋体; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; color: black !important;"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style-type: none; vertical-align: baseline; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; font-size: 16px !important;">江延湖表示，要结合学习内容中关于职业教育发展和科技创新的论述，综合我校实际情况，不仅要注重学生的技能技术培养，培育符合社会发展的高技术技能人才，还要鼓励专业教师深入行业一线掌握先进技术，及时将先进理念、技术引入教育教学，同时要加大对青年教师的培养，组织开展教师技术技能比拼等活动，致力培养出一批教学强师、技能强师，为学校高质量发展注入内生动力。</span></span></p><p><br/></p>